{"tid":242653,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[藝術既野...] 男大生逛藝術展隨手放低個波蘿    隔天竟變成展品","createTime":"2017-05-14T05:40:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-14T06:26:37.000Z","uid":79563,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4dd2fd5925c3c1a73227e735ea626d0591b1accf","tid":242653,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T05:40:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpZpabbU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpZpabbU.jpg&h=839093db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2062115\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2062115&d=zAz8RNAQ9Ot7v23HNjWT3iwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=29cc9346\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2062115&h=1a9c20e8\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2062115</a><br />\n<br />\n英國大學生之前將一顆鳳梨丟在藝術展台後離去，沒想到隔天這顆鳳梨被館方放進玻璃展示櫃裡。（圖擷自DailyMail）<br />\n<br />\n2017-05-09  21:06<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕英國一位大學生之前在參觀藝術館時出於惡作劇，將一個波蘿丟在展台後離去，沒想到隔天回到藝術館卻發現這個波蘿被館方放進玻璃展示櫃裡，他還被評譽為天才。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，英國蘇格蘭22歲大學生格雷（Ruairi Gray）之前花1英鎊（約40元新台幣）買了個波蘿，並將它放進羅伯特戈登大學（Aberdeen's Robert Gordon University）的藝術展展場內。原本格雷只是想看看工作人員多久後才會將波蘿移走，沒想到隔天回展場卻發現波蘿已經被放進玻璃展示櫃，當成藝術品供人參觀。<br />\n<br />\n在波蘿被放入展示櫃的兩天中，共有數百位學生進館參觀，還有許多觀展的講師直言創作此作品的藝術家是位天才。格雷事後幽默表示，他從不認為自己擁有藝術天分，但他現在認為他應該有機會獲得藝術榮譽學位。"},{"pid":"24e17a2bb7d433bbbf6f26a453f30662384b5106","tid":242653,"uid":7846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T05:45:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cbc1e8049a15ace73f9784bf43d14a9482842862","tid":242653,"uid":31254,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T05:45:56.000Z","msg":"藝術=9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00c3b62cea0b03799